Synergetics International Incsaid it has received its first order from China, a 250,000 dlrorder for a flood management system to be used in the Daningand Yuzixi river basins of the Yangtse River.    The company also said it has received Japanese governmentcertification for its satellite transmitter products, allowingusers of Synergetics' remote computer systems to transmit avariety of hydrological and meteorological data via the JapanSpace Agency's GMS satellite.    In addition, it said it has appointed Vaisala KK ofHelsinki as exclkusive distributor of its products throughoutJapan and has awarded Sierra/Misco Inc expanded distributionrights, in the Philippines, Malaysia, Sumatra, Nepal, India,Bengal, Thailand, Singapore and Indonesia. Reuter&#3;